v.no of recs in out form

ColumnTitle.valUnicode: v.no of recs in out form

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from product a where (exists (select * from business_rules b where b.business_rule_code = 300 and b.entity_1_type_CP = 'C' and b.entity_1 = a.product_cu_owner and b.entity_2_type_CP = 'C' and b.entity_2 = :1) or (select d.restrict_with_relation_rule from profile_user c inner join profile d on c.profile_code = d.profile_code where c.entity_id = a.product_cu_owner and c.user_profile_status = 'ACTIVE') != 'Y') :2 :3 :4
